  ],
  "confidence_tier": "high",
  "industry_note": "UNS A91050 / EN AW-1050A / Al99.5 / DIN Al99.5 — 99.5% pure aluminum (non-heat-treatable, R173 fake-variant 제거). O temper: σy 35 / UTS 75 / El 39%. H14 (work-H18 (full hard): σy 145 / UTS 160. 전기 conductor (IACS 60% — Cu의 60%), 화학 plant tank lining, food packaging foil (요구르트 lid, beer can lid). 의도된 variant 보존: O / H14 / H18. 다만 typical H 14 가 σy 105 라 약간 low.",
